issue.body:
The framework code should never use specific behaviour like this:

```php
if (YII_ENV_TEST) {
   throw new ExitException($status);
}

```
https://github.com/yiisoft/yii-core/blame/aa1c38c3e0533c4def419ecdaf53d6a5f8167514/src/base/Application.php#L678

It is responsibility of unit test to decide whether returned response code is expected or not.
